---
title: Buffalo Beef Meatball Subs & Bacon Loaded Fries with Tomato Salsa & Creamy Slaw
description: This sub is the king of sandwiches, packed to bursting with juicy meatballs in a BBQ-sriracha sauce. Don’t ignore the loaded fries,
piled high with golden bacon, corn, and melty cheese. We bow before the might of this delicious meal!
